===Etymology===
From [[w:Henry F. Phillips|Henry F. Phillips]], the name of the inventor of the tool and the screws that it is designed to work with, and [[screwdriver]].

===Noun phrase===
'''Phillips screwdriver''' (''plural'' '''Phillips screwdrivers''')

#A [[screwdriver]] having a [[cross]]-shaped tip rather than the rectangular tip of a standard screwdriver.

